'''Bahía Honda Municipal Museum''' is a [[museum]] located in the 23rd avenue in [[Bahía Honda, Cuba|Bahía Honda]], [[Cuba]]. It was established as a museum on 23 June 1983.<ref>[http://www.cnpc.cult.cu/institucion/384 Museo Municipal de Bahía Honda]</ref>

The museum holds collections on history, weaponry, ethnology, numismatics and archeology.

